title: Judwaa
subTitle: Twin brothers Raja and Prem Malhotra get separated at birth but are reunited by fate to defeat Ratanlal, a local gangster, who wants to destroy the Malhotra family.

title: Ajay
subTitle: Manorama falls in love with Ajay, even though they come from different social backgrounds. They want to get married, but Manorama's uncles try their best to separate the happy couple.

title: Jigariyaa
subTitle: Shaamu, who lives a carefree life, falls in love with a well-educated girl, Raadha. However, circumstances force the young couple to part ways.

title: Dil Jo Na Keh Saka
subTitle: Jay and Siya, friends since childhood, decide to part ways to pursue their ambitions. However, they discover their true feelings for each other when their paths cross years later.

title: Pyar Ishq Aur Mohabbat
subTitle: Yash, Taj and Gaurav fall madly in love with Isha, a beautiful and charming woman. However, Isha is friendly with all three men, unaware of their feelings towards her.

title: Main Tulsi Tere Aangan Ki
subTitle: A wife embraces her husband's illegitimate son as her own in honour of the other woman's memory. However, as time progresses, this starts to seem like a big mistake.

title: Desi Tadka
subTitle: The newest compilation of preppy Punjabi music is played continuously for the viewers with a preference for Indian dance beats.

title: Baaz: A Bird in Danger
subTitle: The police are out on the hunt for a serial killer who targets beautiful women. Their luck changes when a woman who is in love with one of the suspects joins the search.

title: Banjaran
subTitle: The universe offers a Banjara tribe leader's daughter an opportunity to turn her doomed love story into a happily-ever-after with her soulmate.

title: Masoom
subTitle: D K Malhotra leads a peaceful life with his wife and two daughters. But all of this changes when he is forced to bring a boy, who is his son from a previous relationship, home after his mother dies.

title: Ek Rishtaa: The Bond of Love
subTitle: Amid the ideological differences with his father Vijay, Ajay steps up to protect his family from Rajesh's, his brother-in-law's, evil intentions.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: Bahurani
subTitle: Amit wants to marry a modern woman but his parents get him married to a village girl, Madhuri. When Amit refuses to accept her as his wife, Madhuri reinvents herself as Malathi and re-enters his life.

title: Rafoo Chakkar: Fun on the Run
subTitle: Two brothers, Manjeet and Parmeet, run away from their home in order to avoid getting married. Eventually, they lead a life of crime and things take a turn when they get arrested.

title: Ek Nazar
subTitle: Akash, the son of a lawyer, falls in love with a courtesan when he hears her recite one of his poems. However, a series of obstacles and a mysterious murder threaten to break them apart.

title: Maha Badmaash
subTitle: A casino owner is trapped by a gangster and forced to work for him. However, when he refuses to kill a commissioner, the gangster abducts his secretary and sister to blackmail him.

title: Dharam Veer
subTitle: Twin brothers separated at birth become best friends, unaware of their bond as siblings. The queen, their mother, becomes the uniting force as they set out to defeat their evil uncle.

title: Griha Pravesh
subTitle: After Amar falls in love with Sapna, he asks his wife Mansi to divorce him. However, she agrees to do so only if he lets her meet the other woman.

title: Charitraheen
subTitle: Destiny separates two lovers, Inder and Rama, and Inder marries Kamala. However, events take an unprecedented turn when Inder and Rama cross paths again years later.

title: Krodhi
subTitle: Vicky plans to marry Aarti, but his dreams are crushed when an incident causes her to lose her life. Fuelled by revenge, Vicky finds himself going down a dark path.

title: Mann
subTitle: Dev and Priya fall in love despite being engaged to their respective partners and decide to reunite after six months to get married. However, destiny has other plans for them.

title: Pyar Hi Pyar
subTitle: At an orphanage, Kailashnath identifies Vijay as his biological son and takes him home. Years later, a man named Ashok arrives and claims to be Kailashnath's real son.

title: Pyar Hi Pyar
subTitle: At an orphanage, Kailashnath identifies Vijay as his biological son and takes him home. Years later, a man named Ashok arrives and claims to be Kailashnath's real son.

title: Do Chor
subTitle: Tony, a burglar, comes under the radar of suspicion when a series of mysterious thefts bewilder the police. Soon enough, he tries to redeem his honour by going after the real criminal.

title: Sachai Ki Taqat
subTitle: Sagar sets out to exact revenge against Dr Narendra, a smuggler who killed his father. But Sagar is soon framed for the murder of a woman and sent to jail.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: International Crook
subTitle: Rajesh, the superintendent of the police, is happy to meet his old friend, Shekar, in Goa, unaware that he is a smuggler, who is involved in a spree of illegal activities.

title: Yudh
subTitle: A policeman sacrifices his life protecting Savitri and her twins from a gangster. Savitri raises the fallen officer's son as her twins, now separated, grow into a lawyer and a sniper.

title: Kotwal Saab
subTitle: Two siblings drift apart after one of them disapproves of the other's blooming romance with an unknown woman. Eventually, fate reunites them under unexpected circumstances.

title: Sherni
subTitle: Durga, a simple village girl, watches her entire family die at the hands of Thakur. Soon, she picks up the gun and chooses a criminal lifestyle to avenge the death of her loved ones.

title: Dharamyudh
subTitle: Vikram and Pratap, two young friends, live harmoniously. However, things get complicated when Pratap's sister is raped and murdered, and Pratap sets out to exact revenge.

title: Vishwanath
subTitle: Vishwanath, an honest lawyer, is framed and imprisoned due to a gangster. After his release, he sets out to seek revenge and ends up becoming a criminal.

title: Chaand Kaa Tukdaa
subTitle: NRI Shyam comes to India to fulfil the final wish of his late mother who wanted him to marry an Indian girl. Unbeknownst to him, the girl he falls in love with is a pawn in the hands of his enemies.
